18#include <cstdlib>
19#include <type_traits>
20#include <vector>
21#include <string>
22#include <utility>
23
24namespace ZXing {
25
26/**
27* All credits on BigInteger below go to Matt McCutchen, as the code below is extracted/modified from his C++ Big Integer Library (https://mattmccutchen.net/bigint/)
28*/
29class BigInteger
30{
31public:
32 using Block = size_t;
33
34 // The number of bits in a block
35 //static const unsigned int N = 8 * sizeof(Block);
36
37 // Constructs zero.
38 BigInteger() = default;
39
40 template <typename T>
41 BigInteger(T x, typename std::enable_if<std::is_integral<T>::value && std::is_unsigned<T>::value>::type* = nullptr) : mag(1, x) {}
42
43 template <typename T>
44 BigInteger(T x, typename std::enable_if<std::is_integral<T>::value && std::is_signed<T>::value>::type* = nullptr) : negative(x < 0), mag(1, std::abs(x)) {}
45
46 static bool TryParse(const std::string& str, BigInteger& result);
47 static bool TryParse(const std::wstring& str, BigInteger& result);
48
49 bool isZero() const { return mag.empty(); }
50
51 std::string toString() const;
52 int toInt() const;
53
54 inline BigInteger& operator+=(BigInteger&& a) {
55 if (mag.empty())
56 *this = std::move(a);
57 else
58 Add(*this, a, *this);
59 return *this;
60 }
61
62 friend inline BigInteger operator+(const BigInteger& a, const BigInteger& b) {
63 BigInteger c;
64 BigInteger::Add(a, b, c);
65 return c;
66 }
67
68 friend inline BigInteger operator-(const BigInteger& a, const BigInteger& b) {
69 BigInteger c;
70 BigInteger::Subtract(a, b, c);
71 return c;
72 }
73
74 friend inline BigInteger operator*(const BigInteger& a, const BigInteger& b) {
75 BigInteger c;
76 BigInteger::Multiply(a, b, c);
77 return c;
78 }
79
80 static void Add(const BigInteger& a, const BigInteger &b, BigInteger& c);
81 static void Subtract(const BigInteger& a, const BigInteger &b, BigInteger& c);
82 static void Multiply(const BigInteger& a, const BigInteger &b, BigInteger& c);
83 static void Divide(const BigInteger& a, const BigInteger &b, BigInteger& quotient, BigInteger& remainder);
84
85private:
86 bool negative = false;
87 std::vector<Block> mag;
88};
89
90
91} // ZXing
